{"tid":1563743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"假如呢場光復運動失敗。。。","createTime":"2019-09-12T13:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T13:49:40.000Z","uid":48040,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1f002ffd73d22c457e183ef969c68ee6616d524","tid":1563743,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:41:22.000Z","msg":"林鄭話，如果香港順利度過呢場危機，咁就要進行大量改革。<br />\n明眼人都知，言下之意就是要清算啦！<br />\n我地不妨揣測一下，如果光復失敗的話，香港會進行點樣的大清洗：<br />\n媒體：<br />\n-培植更多類似01咁，表面中立甚至淺黃，但實質維護建制利益的媒體（南早係一個唔錯的目標）<br />\n-將連登、立場、蘋果三大毒草連根拔起<br />\n教育：<br />\n-所有干犯非法集會、襲警罪的青年不得入讀大學<br />\n-所有曾經被捕、不管有沒有入罪的教師，將會失去教席，教育局的解釋是&ldquo;不評論個別辦學團體的人事安排決定&rdquo;<br />\n-鼓勵學生督灰，監察教師在課堂上的言行。如果同情示威者的話，教師同樣面臨被革職的處罰<br />\n警權：<br />\n-辱警罪、禁止蒙面的法例快速三讀通過<br />\n-修改《警察通例》，方便鎮壓示威<br />\n<br />\n歡迎繼續補充"},{"pid":"9fffcea1bf2a565103a2e9624711d5c860ce1012","tid":1563743,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:41:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"29e73d560fb637646f55ed413780e222546e4f63","tid":1563743,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:42:36.000Z","msg":"失敗咗，我哋死硬<br />\n我哋今次冇得輸"},{"pid":"dd95b57f1d094282a53ecd74c24983c9aef0f3f1","tid":1563743,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"